rows.label: tlk44310182_04_msg0002
rows.name:
A small platoon headed up the Norb
Mountains for marching practice.

rows.label: tlk44310182_04_msg0003
rows.name:
But they took a wrong turn and ended
up in Volff hunting grounds. Looks like
they took a bit of battering...

rows.label: tlk44310182_04_msg0004
rows.name:
We're in the middle of assembling
a rescue squad, but we're a little
understaffed right now...

rows.label: tlk44310182_04_msg0005
rows.name:
Hmm? You'll lend us some of your
mercs?

rows.label: tlk44310182_04_msg0006
rows.name:
...Sorry to have dragged you into this.
We won't forget your help.
